extendedInfo.description: Statistics Express Pro allows users to perform a few useful statistical analyzes on an android phone.Key features include:1. Calculate the mean, standard deviation (SD) and standard error mean (SEM) from any number of numbers;2. Perform paired or unpaired student t test. Calculate t and p values;3. Allow users to save data and reload the previously saved data;4. A custom keypad is included for easy data entry;5. Users can send data and analysis results via E-mail.The Statistics Express Pro does not contain any advertisement. Thanks for using the application.
